The '''Bantha Clan''' was an [[Jedi Initiate/Legends|initiate]] training clan of the [[New Jedi Order]] named after the [[Bantha/Legends|bantha]], a creature found throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. In [[35 ABY/Legends|35 ABY]], it consisted mostly of students who were the between the ages of ten to twelve.<ref name="Legacy of the Force: Inferno">''[[Legacy of the Force: Inferno]]''</ref> In [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]] [[Vekki]], a member of Bantha Clan, was saved by [[Zekk]] during the [[Battle of Ossus (Second Galactic Civil War)|raid on the Jedi Academy]]. They were later rescued and taken to the [[Jedi Outpost]] on [[Endor (planet)/Legends|Endor's]] [[Moon/Legends|Sanctuary Moon]].

